vortex + no diffusion:
   exact horizontal integration (dt -> 0)
  
constant vertical diffusion profile:
   sqrt(t) vertical dispersal
   even distribution of particles
 
non constant vertical diffusion profile + reflective BC:
   even vertical distribution test
   
constant horizontal diffusion profile + box domain + reflective BC:
   sqrt(t) horizontal dispersal
   even horizontal distribution test



